President Dr John Magufuli has, with effect from today, appointed Judge Sivangilwa Mwangesi  to be the  Commissioner of Ethics Secretariat, filling  the vacancy following the death of Judge Harold Nsekela that occurred early this month . According to the press statemet issued by the State House today, Judge Mwangesi will be sworn in on Thursday(December 24, 2020) at Chamwino State House in Dodoma.  